name: Core Icons Pack (preview)
description:
Core Icons Pack is a part of Core Icons Library such made for everyone who builds UI/UX design, SAAS products, Web and Mobile apps.


Highlights

  • Based on 24px pixel-grid
  • All shapes are vector
  • Easily to change scale and tone
  • 1.5px line stroke
  • Fluid styles
  • Integration into best apps (IconJar included)
